
# 1. Product Overview

AI Interview Coach is a cloud-native, AI-powered interview and exam preparation platform designed to bridge the employability gap among graduates. The system provides multimodal evaluation (text, voice, and video) to simulate real-world interviews and competitive exams.

The platform supports both:

* **B2C (Individual Users)** – Students, graduates, working professionals
* **B2B (Institutions & Corporates)** – Colleges, training centers, HR departments

The product aims to provide personalized feedback, adaptive difficulty, and structured performance analytics.

---

# 2. Problem Statement

Despite rapid educational growth in India, nearly **45–50% of graduates lack job readiness**. Existing platforms:

* Only evaluate written answers
* Do not analyze body language or speech behavior
* Lack adaptive learning
* Do not integrate interview + exam prep together
* Do not provide personalized improvement pathways

There is no unified system combining:

* Mock Interviews
* Competitive Exam Practice
* Voice & Visual Behavioral Analysis
* Skill Gap Mapping
* Real-time Feedback
* Institutional Monitoring

AI Interview Coach addresses this gap.

---

# 3. Goals & Objectives

### Primary Goals

1. Provide realistic AI-driven mock interviews.
2. Evaluate multimodal behavior (speech, emotion, posture).
3. Offer structured performance reports.
4. Provide adaptive difficulty.
5. Support both B2C and B2B use cases.

### Success Metrics (KPIs)

| Metric                         | Target                        |
| ------------------------------ | ----------------------------- |
| Mock interview completion rate | > 75%                         |
| User retention (30 days)       | > 50%                         |
| Avg. report generation time    | < 30 sec                      |
| Institutional adoption rate    | 10+ colleges in Year 1        |
| Confidence score improvement   | 20% increase after 4 sessions |

